---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="container">
		<header class="fade-in-up">
			<div class="logo-container">
				<img src="/assets/logo.svg" alt="Aeternum Logo" class="logo" />
			</div>
			<nav>
				<a href="/catalog" class="nav-link-vertical">目録</a>
			</nav>
		</header>

		<main>
			<section class="hero fade-in-up">
				<div class="structure-bg"></div>
				<div class="hero-subtitle">構造と表現</div>
				<h1 class="hero-title">蒐集庵</h1>
			</section>

			<section class="concept fade-in-up">
				<p>
					この世に「非合理」は存在しない。<br />
					短期的・局所的な視点を超え、<br />
					長い時間軸の中で、<br />
					意味は静かに接続される。
				</p>
				<div class="vertical-text">
					<p>
						もの言わぬ古き物たち。<br />
						その背後にある構造。<br />
						時間に耐えうる思想。<br />
						<br />
						ここは、それらを蒐集し、<br />
						編み直すための庵。
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>

		<footer class="fade-in-up">
			<p>&copy; 2026 Aeternum. All Rights Reserved.</p>
		</footer>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.container {
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: flex-start;
		margin-bottom: 8rem;
	}

	.logo {
		width: 120px;
		filter: brightness(0) saturate(100%) invert(32%) sepia(16%) border-left(10px) hue-rotate(69deg) brightness(91%) contrast(85%); /* Approximate Evergreen */
	}

	.nav-link-vertical {
		writing-mode: vertical-rl;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--accent-primary);
		letter-spacing: 0.3em;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		transition: opacity 0.3s;
	}

	.nav-link-vertical:hover {
		opacity: 0.7;
	}

	.hero {
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: 10rem;
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		font-size: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.5em;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.hero-title {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--accent-primary);
	}

	.concept {
		line-height: 2.5;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	}

	.vertical-text {
		writing-mode: vertical-rl;
		margin-top: 4rem;
		height: 400px;
		color: var(--accent-secondary);
	}

	footer {
		margin-top: 10rem;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--text-muted);
		padding-top: 2rem;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
	}
</style>
